com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Models

Class Participant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Models.Participant

  • public class Participant
extends java.lang.Object
    Participant model to describe the attributes of the participant. Each participant upon signup will hold their own personal arrays of mood events, followers, following, and pending requests. Currently the last three are out of service until later development. Participants will have their own unique ID upon creation. Followers/Following are kept to their names. When required, pull profile of the names that they would have picked
    See Also:
    LoginActivity
